    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those portions of jambs of an opening or recess which are visible from the face of the wall back to the frame or other structure which may be placed between the jambs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
